  private HeaderClass header;
  private PayloadClass payload;
  private String fileID;
}
```
Using `@JsonProperty`
```Java
public class Response {
  // index will control the order of field
  @JsonProperty(index = 2)
  private HeaderClass header;
  @JsonProperty(index = 1)
